description: This easy to set up Dog agility tunnel measures 16'l x 2'w x 2'h & comes with a convenient carry bag. Stakes are included so the tunnel can be secured to the ground using the attached grommets. Use the tunnel to improve a dog's Speed & dexterity while teaching obedience. Using the tunnel regularly as a training tool will also help develop the owner/Dog relationship. By Trademark Innovations.
